{"tid":2493690,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大移民討論區 4","createTime":"2021-04-18T06:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T05:18:33.000Z","uid":56984,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7a29e6858a7b6768d7b5f7f673f1e276d2a0f79c","tid":2493690,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"原PO：<br />\n<br />\n加拿大移民討論區<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2400030\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2400030</a><br />\n<br />\n加拿大移民討論區 2<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2417524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2417524</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n加拿大移民討論區 3<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2454438\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2454438</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa7854477efcaf2c85c8d9d160d0c66dec27307b","tid":2493690,"uid":56984,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:05:53.000Z","msg":"#懶人包  3月16號 更新<br />\n全程埋單6000HKD有找<br />\n申請1530 驗身2170 學歷1380 指紋510<br />\n齊文件申請全程不多於兩小時<br />\n*唔講錢，教你移民加拿大*<br />\n<br />\n申請無需Job Offer及IELTS<br />\n新申請有機會被要求良民證<br />\n<br />\n本Scheme申請期至2023年2月止<br />\n最遲幾時要Grad? 2023年2月 持有有效證書<br />\n有效期：❓❓❓<br />\n<br />\n因疫情關係，未受聘者暫時未能入境，自行衡量申請Visa時間<br />\n現時到埗後亦需自費隔離三天 約2000CAD<br />\n於4月30日後入境不需自費集中隔離<br />\n仍需自行安排14日自我隔離<br />\n🌍入境限制相關新聞🌍<br />\n<br />\n👌🏻大流程 缺☝🏻不可：<br />\n1️⃣網上交表+💳付款<br />\nHong Kong Visa 有D位要跟公告指示填<br />\n🌍網上申請入口 🌏<br />\n*交表後才會驗身，只需要Download Health Form Tick Yes完上載*<br />\n*閒日等兩星期，星期六等兩個月*<br />\n*可因應自己需要預早Book位*<br />\n/bodycheck@IVECodeCat_bot <br />\n2️⃣加國以外Diploma➡️學歷證明👨&zwj;🎓（五年內有效）<br />\nDegree or above不再需要ECA<br />\n（唯移民局有權要求）<br />\n搞邊款: ECA Application for IRCC<br />\n搞幾耐: 自稱35個working day 及早行動<br />\nDelivery Method：想慳錢就Standard，移民局會有e-copy<br />\nWES(最普遍) CES ICAS IQAS BCIT <br />\n/eca@IVECodeCat_bot <br />\n3️⃣驗身+打指紋，後述<br />\nTLDR驗身有效一年 指紋有效十年<br />\n/biometric@IVECodecat_bot<br />\n/policecert@IVECodecat_bot<br />\n/bodycheck@IVECodecat_bot<br />\n<br />\nHD/AD可以先申請，同時搞ECA<br />\n驗身要等移民局比信你<br />\n但你可以Book定驗身先因為期爆<br />\n<br />\n網上申請需要準備 (➡️上載至)：<br />\n💳信用卡 - 用黎比錢<br />\n🛂Passport封面及所有內頁 ➡️Passport<br />\n👨&zwj;🎓學位成績單 ➡️Proof of Job Requirement<br />\n📄CV一份 - 講解工作經驗 ➡️CV/Resume<br />\n📷電子版大頭證件相 ➡️Digital Photo<br />\n📄空白PDF一份大字寫 &rdquo;Not Applicable&ldquo;, for<br />\n- Employment Reference Letter<br />\n- Letter from current employer<br />\n- Employment record<br />\n- Employment contract<br />\n👶出世紙(Optional, Good to have)<br />\n 💏結婚證書(已婚者適用)<br />\n*PDF限4MB內 實試32頁full color要200DPI+走白邊*<br />\n*網上申請未需要驗身，只需download佢份PDF填Yes(如果在港)*<br />\n*可以先Book UMP，然後等驗身信，通常一個月左右有*<br />\n<br />\nPDF太大點算好? <br />\n💃🏻可Crop走空白位🕺🏻<br />\n💃🏻改低DPI，96以上已接受🕺🏻<br />\n<br />\n完成網上Visa Application後：<br />\n1️⃣申請*Transcript成績表* 後申請學歷證明 &quot;For IRCC&quot; (見新聞內文)<br />\n一定要買一份新既，學校信封+蓋印+密封，唔好手癢開左佢<br />\n(A)院校直接寄往機構<br />\n(B)申請人自行寄回機構 - 搵另一個信封入落去再寄<br />\n不接受 *畢業證書*❌ <br />\n點擊獲取院方資訊 👉 /eca@IVECodeCat_bot<br />\n<br />\n2️⃣等出驗身信➡️Book驗身➡️佐敦/中環 UMP<br />\n☎️打去約3950 8868，web廢的☎️<br />\n🔍驗身內容 🔍<br />\n帶：Passport，Form-1017E<br />\n<br />\n3️⃣交錢等通知➡️預約打指紋➡️炮台山理文<br />\n比完錢Upload完記得Next<br />\nVFS預約連結<br />\n帶：Passport，預約信，指紋信<br />\n<br />\nBudget（CA 1:6 港元）：<br />\n香港UMP驗身 HKD2170<br />\nVisa Fee CA$255 = $1530<br />\n學歷證明 CA$220+10 = $1380<br />\n指紋費 CA$85 = $510<br />\n機票 9月單程 800CAD<br />\n頭半年食宿 租樓平均1500-2200CAD/Mo x6<br />\n有機會自費檢疫3天 2000CAD<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n📝表格代號一覽<br />\n1295 - Application for WP (主申請表)<br />\n5753 - Request for medical exam<br />\n5475 - Authority to release personal info<br />\n5707 - Family Information Form (如需簽名要Print)<br />\n1071 - 驗身信<br />\n<br />\n📤香港郵政服務現況(郵寄學歷至機構)📤<br />\n  往🇨🇦：只限EMS/平郵 ； ❌空郵"},{"pid":"8f4c460c8e17578cc908ded338977fbd7a453b66","tid":2493690,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:06:37.000Z","msg":"內有懶人包<br />\n今期流行 流行大專生移民 🎤<br />\n怎樣移民 都要睇完Pin先過問<br />\n<br />\n谷規：<br />\n自由討論 禁止賣廣告 禁止Agent<br />\n禁止鬥黃<br />\n<br />\n懶人包Link; Read Before Ask:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/c/1290122412/9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1290122412%2F9&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RCLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=3557d785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1290122412/9</a><br />\n<br />\n本谷Link<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/IfOKhh-NkIuGRs8H\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FIfOKhh-NkIuGRs8H&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RCLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=40f422d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/IfOKhh-NkIuGRs8H</a>"},{"pid":"fdab71f3b73bd4d4f8d37a266975d4f6c7f4a1d6","tid":2493690,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:08:05.000Z","msg":"reference by TG group<br />\n<br />\n@如孩兒能伏於曾女的肩膀，進要下車"},{"pid":"9c3af76cb6972c22886b38a79a75ea8e53648dcc","tid":2493690,"uid":75583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:22:45.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"efa76feb442ccd1c694f6afc8425a3c0ea5584d2","tid":2493690,"uid":68231,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:41:47.000Z","msg":"我係2016年畢業, 換言之今年就係最後一年<br />\n但係2021年參考邊一日作為deadline呢?<br />\n睇返畢業證書邊月邊日之前申請? 定係睇D咩野"},{"pid":"389244da439b49c62a511d926ebf4cf4337af97f","tid":2493690,"uid":229335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efa76feb442ccd1c694f6afc8425a3c0ea5584d2","tid":2493690,"uid":68231,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:41:47.000Z","msg":"我係2016年畢業, 換言之今年就係最後一年<br />\n但係2021年參考邊一日作為deadline呢?<br />\n睇返畢業證書邊月邊日之前申請? 定係睇D咩野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:43:11.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"2757adf7dc8c72507e64f732b3c31831d830c2d8","tid":2493690,"uid":266555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"efa76feb442ccd1c694f6afc8425a3c0ea5584d2","tid":2493690,"uid":68231,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:41:47.000Z","msg":"我係2016年畢業, 換言之今年就係最後一年<br />\n但係2021年